If you'd like to contribute to the pure:dyne project, please contact us via the [http://lists.goto10.org/cgi-bin/mailman/listinfo/puredyne pure:dyne Mailing List]. We are always looking for skilled people who can help out with development, packaging software and writing documentation.


























